msgctxt "an7.55:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.55:0.2"
msgid "6. Abyākatavagga "
msgstr "6. The Undeclared Points "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.55:0.3"
msgid "55. Purisagatisutta "
msgstr "55. Places People Are Reborn "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: Satta ca → satta (si, pts1) | satta ca kho (mr)
msgctxt "an7.55:1.1"
msgid "“Satta ca, bhikkhave, purisagatiyo desessāmi anupādā ca parinibbānaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you seven places people are reborn, and extinguishment by not grasping. "

msgctxt "an7.55:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.55:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” the mendicants replied. "

msgctxt "an7.55:1.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.55:1.5"
msgid "“katamā ca, bhikkhave, satta purisagatiyo? "
msgstr "“And what are the seven places people are reborn? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.71, sc2
msgctxt "an7.55:2.1"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ paṭipanno hoti: "
msgstr "Take a mendicant who practices like this: "

msgctxt "an7.55:2.2"
msgid "‘no cassa no ca me siyā, na bhavissati na me bhavissati, yadatthi yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ pajahāmī’ti upekkhaṃ paṭilabhati. "
msgstr "‘It might not be, and it might not be mine. It will not be, and it will not be mine. I am giving up what exists, what has come to be.’ They gain equanimity. "

msgctxt "an7.55:2.3"
msgid "So bhave na rajjati, sambhave na rajjati, atthuttari padaṃ santaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "They’re not attached to life, or to creating a new life. And they see with right wisdom that there is a peaceful state beyond. "

msgctxt "an7.55:2.4"
msgid "Tañca khvassa padaṃ na sabbena sabbaṃ sacchikataṃ hoti, tassa na sabbena sabbaṃ mānānusayo pahīno hoti, na sabbena sabbaṃ bhavarāgānusayo pahīno hoti, na sabbena sabbaṃ avijjānusayo pahīno hoti. "
msgstr "But they haven’t completely realized that state. They haven’t totally given up the underlying tendencies of conceit, attachment to life, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "an7.55:2.5"
msgid "So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti. "
msgstr "With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished between one life and the next. "

#. VAR: divasaṃsantatte → divasasantatte (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.55:2.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, divasaṃsantatte ayokapāle haññamāne papaṭikā nibbattitvā nibbāyeyya. "
msgstr "Suppose you struck an iron pot that had been heated all day. Any spark that flew off would be extinguished. "

msgctxt "an7.55:2.7"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ paṭipanno hoti: "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant who practices like this … "

